I"T<p>Drakensang is a traditional, classic,  story driven party RPG for PC. Based on the German Pen and Paper RPG “The Dark Eye” (“Das Schwarze Auge”) three parts have been released:</p>

<ul>
  <li>2008 Drakensang The Dark Eye</li>
  <li>2009 Drakensang River of Time</li>
  <li>2010 Drakensang Philleason´s Secret</li>
</ul>

